craterdog.notary

Class NotaryCertificate

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.smart.SmartObject<NotaryCertificate>
      • craterdog.notary.NotaryCertificate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    craterdog.core.Composite, Comparable<NotaryCertificate>

    public final class NotaryCertificate
extends craterdog.smart.SmartObject<NotaryCertificate>
    This class defines a public digital certificate that can be used to verify a notary seal created using the associated private notary key.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
